SUMMARY:Chelsea Baila Social Club
DESCRIPTION:✨️ Chelsea Baila Social Club is back! ✨️\nOn select Saturdays we will turn Chelsea Market into a dancefloor for one more season.\nWe start at 7pm\, with a free salsa class\, open to everyone\, no partner needed. 💃🕺\nAt 7.45ish\, we start with social dancing with the one and only – 🎧 DJ Gagou spinning the very best of salsa ☆ timba ☆ bachata ☆ y mas! 🔥\nThe event is free for everyone. Hope you can join us! 🥳\nThe Fall 2025 dates:\nSeptember 27\nOctober 4\, 18\nNovember 1\, 15\, 29\nDecember 13
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/chelsea-baila-social-club/2026-03-14/
LOCATION:Chelsea Market\, 75 9th Ave\, Chelsea\, Manhattan\, NY\, 10011\, United States
END:VEVENT
