SUMMARY:Bachata ConeXion Saturdays 'Cosmic ConeXion'
DESCRIPTION:🖤💛 Bachateros of Melbourne City — Get Ready for COSMIC CONEXION! 💫\n.\n✨ Cosmic ConeXion is here! Step into a universe of yellow energy\, black hearts\, and cool star vibes for a night of bachata\, connection\, and cosmic feels 💃🕺\n.\n📅 Date: Saturday\, 14th of March\n.\n🕗 Time:\n8:00 pm — Bachata Workshop (Open Level)\n9:00 pm – 1:00 am — Social Dancing\n.\n📍 Location:\nSokol Melbourne Inc\n497 Queensberry Street\, North Melbourne\n.\n🎶 Music Policy:\n70% Bachata • 30% Salsa • + Touch of Kizomba & Zouk\n.\n👔 Dress Code:\n💛 Yellow & Black 🖤\nAdd hearts\, stars\, and cosmic flair — dress to impress ✨\n.\n🎧 DJ Lineup:\nDJ Hong Starr\, DJ JT (from Spain)\, DJ Spanky\n.\n💃🕺 Walk-in Prices:\n8:00 pm Workshop + Social — $22\n9:00 pm Social Only — $18\nAfter 11:30 pm — $13\n.\n💻 Online Prices (Save $$):\n8:00 pm Workshop + Social — $18\n9:00 pm till 1:00 am Social — $14\n.\n🎫 Limited Tickets Online — Book Now & Save!\nhttps://www.trybooking.com/DJSDG\n.\n📲 Stay Updated: Click “Going” on the event!\n.\n🌟 Join the Bachata ConeXion Family and experience that Cosmic ConeXion feeling!\n.\n🌍 Connecting the Bachata Community of Melbourne\n.\n🎉 Everyone Welcome! Beginners\, experienced dancers\, first-timers — we got you!\n.\n📸 Instagram: @bachataconexion\n✉ Become a Member: bachataconexion18@gmail.com \n(FREE to join)\n.\n⚠ Friendly Reminder:\nBy attending you acknowledge:\n✔ You are fit to participate\n✔ Refund/credit available for cancellations (online bookings only)\n✔ Organisers/instructors are not liable for injuries\n✔ Photos & videos may be taken for marketing/social use\n.\n🌌💛 Let’s turn the dance floor cosmic in Yellow & Black — see you under the stars! 💛🌌
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/%f0%9f%92%ab-bachata-conexion-saturdays-cosmic-conexion-%f0%9f%92%ab/
LOCATION:497-499 Queensberry St\, 497-499 Queensberry St\, North Melbourne\, VIC\, 3053\, Australia
CATEGORIES:Melbourne
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/636331291_1497081385761078_7931092277695828396_n.jpg
END:VEVENT
