SUMMARY:Echale Austin Social - Texas All-Star Edition
DESCRIPTION:🌎 𝐄𝐂𝐇𝐀𝐋𝐄 𝐀𝐔𝐒𝐓𝐈𝐍 𝐐𝐔𝐀𝐓𝐄𝐑𝐋𝐘 𝐒𝐎𝐂𝐈𝐀𝐋 🌍 \n🤠🌵⭐ 𝐓𝐄𝐗𝐀𝐒 𝐀𝐋𝐋-𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑 𝐄𝐃𝐈𝐓𝐈𝐎𝐍 ⭐🌵🤠 \n✨ ECHALE is back on March 14th — and we’re starting the year strong as we kick off our FIRST quarterly event with a 𝙏𝙀𝙓𝘼𝙎 𝘼𝙇𝙇-𝙎𝙏𝘼𝙍 𝙏𝙃𝙀𝙈𝙀\, featuring standout artists\, instructors\, and performers from 𝘼𝙪𝙨𝙩𝙞𝙣\, 𝘿𝙖𝙡𝙡𝙖𝙨\, 𝙎𝙖𝙣 𝘼𝙣𝙩𝙤𝙣𝙞𝙤\, 𝙖𝙣𝙙 𝙃𝙤𝙪𝙨𝙩𝙤𝙣. One night. One state. All the Texas flavor. \n𝙀𝙭𝙥𝙚𝙧𝙞𝙚𝙣𝙘𝙚 𝘼𝙪𝙨𝙩𝙞𝙣’𝙨 𝙊𝙉𝙇𝙔 𝙩𝙧𝙪𝙚 𝙩𝙬𝙤-𝙧𝙤𝙤𝙢 𝙨𝙤𝙘𝙞𝙖𝙡\, 𝙙𝙚𝙡𝙞𝙫𝙚𝙧𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙛𝙚𝙨𝙩𝙞𝙫𝙖𝙡-𝙨𝙩𝙮𝙡𝙚 𝙙𝙖𝙣𝙘𝙚 𝙫𝙞𝙗𝙚𝙨 𝙬𝙞𝙩𝙝 100% 𝙎𝙖𝙡𝙨𝙖 𝙞𝙣 𝙤𝙣𝙚 𝙧𝙤𝙤𝙢 & 100% 𝘽𝙖𝙘𝙝𝙖𝙩𝙖 𝙞𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙤𝙩𝙝𝙚𝙧. Two rooms\, two energies\, one unforgettable night — happening quarterly on the second Saturday of the month at our home\, Austin Uptown Dance Studio. \n𝐁𝐘𝐎𝐁 🍾 | 𝐅𝐫𝐞𝐞 𝐏𝐚𝐫𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐠 🚗 | 𝐒𝐦𝐨𝐨𝐭𝐡 𝐃𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐅𝐥𝐨𝐨𝐫𝐬 🕺| 𝐓𝐨𝐩 𝐃𝐉𝐬 🎧| 𝐈𝐧𝐜𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝐝𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐞𝐫𝐬 💃 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐧𝐨𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐨𝐩 𝐠𝐨𝐨𝐝 𝐯𝐢𝐛𝐞𝐬 ✨ — this is Echale Austin\, where the dance floor speaks for itself. \n⭐𝐒𝐚𝐥𝐬𝐚 𝐎𝐍𝟐 𝐛𝐲 𝐉𝐨𝐡𝐚𝐧 & 𝐀𝐥𝐲𝐬𝐬𝐚 (𝗧𝗶𝗺𝗯𝗮 𝗧𝘂𝗺𝗯𝗮𝗼)⭐\n𝘓𝘦𝘷𝘦𝘭: 𝘐𝘯𝘵𝘦𝘳𝘮𝘦𝘥𝘪𝘢𝘵𝘦\nJohan & Alyssa Ibanez of Timba Tumbao Dance Company are one of Texas’ most iconic Salsa couples. Based in the Dallas area\, this powerhouse duo has spent the past decade training dancers of all levels with heart\, depth\, and unmatched musicality. Their approach goes far beyond steps and counts—they dive into the history and rhythms of Salsa to help dancers feel the music and express it through movement and connection. Catch their special workshop at Echale\, where they’ll be teaching a 1-hour Salsa footwork & partnerwork class at 9PM — salseros you don’t want to miss! \n⭐ 𝐁𝐚𝐜𝐡𝐚𝐭𝐚 𝐂𝐥𝐚𝐬𝐬 𝐛𝐲 𝐒𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐨𝐧 & 𝐄𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐤 (𝐅𝐫𝐚𝐦𝐛𝐨𝐲𝐚𝐧)⭐\n𝘓𝘦𝘷𝘦𝘭: 𝘖𝘱𝘦𝘯\nGet ready for a dynamic Bachata class led by Sharon & Erick\, two of Framboyán Dance Company’s most recognized and respected instructors from San Antonio. Known for their musicality\, smooth partner connection\, and clear teaching style\, this class will focus on practical partnerwork you can take straight to the social floor. Perfect for dancers looking to level up their flow\, confidence\, and connection. \n⭐𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐒𝐎𝐂𝐈𝐀𝐋 ⭐\n-Saturday\, March 14th\n-9:00p: Salsa Class by Johan & Alyssa\n-9:00p: Bachata Class by Sharon & Erick\n-10:00p: Social Dancing until 2am\n**No partner required for workshops!** \n​​⭐𝐄𝐂𝐇𝐀𝐋𝐄 𝐒𝐀𝐋𝐒𝐈𝐓𝐀 ⭐\n**100% Salsa Room!**\n-Music By: 𝐃𝐉 𝐁𝐢𝐠 𝐉 𝐀𝐓𝐗 & 𝐃𝐉 𝐈𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐚 (Oneysis)\n-Spinning only the best salsa all night long! \n⭐𝐄𝐂𝐇𝐀𝐋𝐄 𝐁𝐀𝐂𝐇𝐀𝐓𝐀 ⭐\n**100% Bachata Room!**\n-Music by: 𝐃𝐉 𝐑𝐚𝐲 & 𝐃𝐉 𝐌𝐮𝐧𝐨𝐳\n-Spinning Traditional & Modern bachata hits! \n⭐𝐏𝐄𝐑𝐅𝐎𝐑𝐌𝐀𝐍𝐂𝐄𝐒 & 𝐆𝐔𝐄𝐒𝐓 𝐀𝐑𝐓𝐈𝐒𝐓𝐒 ⭐\n-Brian & Alex (Dallas)\n-Johan & Alyssa (Dallas)\n-Timba Tumbao (Dallas)\n-Framboyan (San Antonio & Austin)\n-Oneysis (San Antonio)\n-Yayita Finin (Houston) \n⭐𝐓𝐈𝐂𝐊𝐄𝐓𝐒 ⭐\n-Social Only: $17 (Presale)* / $20 (Door)\n-Social + Class: $25 (Presale)* / $30 (Door)\n-College Students: $15 (Class & Social)**\n-Table Reservation for 4: $25\n*𝘗𝘳𝘦𝘴𝘢𝘭𝘦 𝘦𝘯𝘥𝘴 𝘰𝘯 𝘦𝘷𝘦𝘯𝘵 𝘥𝘢𝘺\, 𝘢𝘭𝘭 𝘴𝘢𝘭𝘦𝘴 𝘢𝘳𝘦 𝘯𝘰𝘯-𝘳𝘦𝘧𝘶𝘯𝘥𝘢𝘣𝘭𝘦 & 𝘯𝘰𝘯-𝘵𝘳𝘢𝘯𝘴𝘧𝘦𝘳𝘢𝘣𝘭𝘦\n**𝘚𝘵𝘶𝘥𝘦𝘯𝘵𝘴 𝘮𝘶𝘴𝘵 𝘴𝘩𝘰𝘸 𝘤𝘶𝘳𝘳𝘦𝘯𝘵 𝘴𝘤𝘩𝘦𝘥𝘶𝘭𝘦 𝘢𝘵 𝘥𝘰𝘰𝘳 \n⭐𝐋𝐎𝐂𝐀𝐓𝐈𝐎𝐍 ⭐\nAustin Uptown Dance\n8868 Research Blvd #706\,\nAustin\, TX 78758 \n⭐𝐌𝐄𝐃𝐈𝐀 𝐓𝐄𝐀𝐌 ⭐\n📸 Photos by ZB Imagery & 🎥 Video by Dot Creativ! They’ll be capturing complimentary photos and videos throughout the night. Tips are welcomed! 😊 (No professional photography or video allowed without permission!) \n⭐𝐁𝐘𝐎𝐁 ⭐\nPlenty of free Parking! 🅿️\nWater\, cups & ice available for sale🥤🧊\nTable Reservations for you & your crew!\nWe hope to see you there!! 🙏\n-Echale Salsita Crew ❤️‍🔥 \n[By attending this event\, you consent to being photographed and filmed. Attendees are also agreeing to abide by our code of conduct. If you are ever the subject of or witness to harassment at one of our events\, please notify staff or report the incident via our feedback form → https://forms.gle/o6EESs3wh9DnYGMz9]
