DESCRIPTION:Blen Blen – Every 2nd Saturday! \nRegular Classes \n\n8PM: Mambo\n8PM: Cuban Salsa\n8PM: Hustle\n8PM: Bachata\n\nEvening Shows \n\n9pm to 10pm – Evening Show and Reception\n\nSocial (4 rooms) \n\nSalsa Room\nBachata Room\nCuban Salsa Room\nHustle Room\n\nTickets \n– Please Zelle us at info@blenblenla.com (include name/email) \n– Or Venmo at @gozalo \nRegular Classes (Soho Dance LA) \nPERFORMERS \nIf you’d like to perform\, please contact us to get a performer pass \n(includes all workshops and social): \nFacebook: BlenBlenLA \nInstagram: blenblenla \nwww.blenblenla.com for more details.
